Recommended Open APIs for Job Flow:
1. Job Listings APIs:
GitHub Jobs API (free) - https://jobs.github.com/api

Reed.co.uk API (free tier available)

Adzuna API (free tier)

USAJOBS API (US government jobs, free)

2. Additional Useful APIs:
OpenAI API - Generate job descriptions, candidate summaries

Resume Parser APIs (like Sovren, Affinda - free trials)

Calendar API (Google Calendar) - Schedule interviews

Email API (Resend, SendGrid) - Send notifications